Notes: Marian rallies from 58-49 deficit with 2:44 to play, taking 59-58 lead on two
FT's by Sarah Olewinski with 37 seconds left. Bailey Grayvold hits 1 of 2 FTs
with 17 sec left in regulation to tie game and send to OT. Marian takes lead
for good on 3-ptr by Sarah Albert making it 64-62 with 1:11 left in OT.
